id: pm-a7o4
title: First-party baseline profile package built on public SDK primitives
description: Provide an installable first-party exemplar package that dogfoods public SDK primitives for a complete project-management archetype/profile.
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 2
tags[6]: "area:packages","area:sdk",customization,dogfood,package-author,profiles
